@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ftbzty(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(v1)
    tmp = 0.58
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin(v2))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp((tmp + 0.27 + v2 + 0.85)))
    v1 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.48) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.02)) / 0.37)
    data[tid] = v0
